gojira_olympic-paris-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gojira_olympic-paris-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201925078 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; color: #000000; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Segoe UI Web', Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira</a>表示，在 2024 年奥运会开幕式上代表“整个金属界”时，他们感到面临压力。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/gojira-fortitude-review-2928116">Gojira – “Fortitude”评论：推动沉重岩石前进的地震金属愤怒者</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-gojira-perform-ah-ca-ira-in-the-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778455">周五（7 月 26 日）在巴黎举行的颁奖典礼上，法国重金属乐队与实验歌剧歌手玛丽娜·维奥蒂 (Marina Viotti) 一起表演了爆炸性的《啊，恰伊拉》(Ah, Ça Ira)</a> 。</p><p>这首歌被翻译为“一切都会好起来”，在法国大革命期间流行，并被包含在仪式的“自由”部分，强调法国的政治行动和自由的历史。</p><p>乐队出现在一座城堡的一侧，周围环绕着火焰和代表鲜血的红色飘带。他们创造了历史，成为第一支在奥运会开幕式上表演的金属乐队。他们的表演是在献给<em>《悲惨世界》</em>的部分之后进行的，紧接着被斩首的玛丽·安托瓦内特正在唱歌。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="in" dir="ltr"> Gojira <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/paris2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#paris2024</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ceremoniedouverture?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ceremoniedouverture</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/OpeningCeremony?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#OpeningCeremony</a> <a href="https://t.co/9TYBMMjiCE">pic.twitter.com/9TYBMMjiCE</a></p><p> — 约翰 (@johjohbat) <a href="https://twitter.com/johjohbat/status/1816901900345692394?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 7 月 26 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>现在，乐队主唱乔·杜普兰蒂尔在接受<em><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/article/opening-ceremony-heavy-metal-band-gojira.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《纽约时报》</a></em>采访时解释说，参加演出让乐队感受到了在世界上最大的电视观众之一面前代表这一流派及其追随者的压力。</p><p>杜普兰蒂埃表示，他希望这场表演成为“世界舞台上整个金属界”的骄傲，并补充说，考虑到这首歌与革命时期的联系，这首歌特别合适。</p><p> “这是法国历史上一个非常血腥的时代，”他说。 “所以它非常金属。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C95oFxrAd_q/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.